connectshares-antix (0.1.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Modified connectshares, connectshares-config, disconnectshares, to employ user specified terminal emulator plus associated parameters, and default to using x-terminal-emulator in case of an invalid terminal emulator being specified.
  * Created $HOME/.config/connectshares/launcher.conf to hold user specifiable terminal options.  Set urxvt as default.
  * Minor modification to window size in connectshares.sh, that advises it must be started via sudo
  * Modified connectshares, connectshares-config, disconnectshares, to enable them to start the main scripts when in console and GUI modes.  It is now optional to append the .sh suffix when running in console mode.
  * Created $HOME/.config/roxterm.sourceforge.net/Profiles/Connectshares for optional use in launcher.conf
  * Updated version number to 7 for connectshares, connectshares.sh, connectshares-config, connectshares-config.sh, disconnectshares, disconnectshare.sh

 -- anticapitalista <antiX@operamail.com>  Sun, 09 Feb 2014 16:35:00 +0200


